 api_key (str, optional): An alternative parameter for providing the API key. Defaults to None.\n    base_url (str, optional): The base URL for the NIM. Use this to switch to an on-premises NIM.\n    max_tokens (int, optional): The maximum number of tokens to generate. Defaults to 1024.\n    **kwargs: Additional keyword arguments.\n\nAPI Keys:\n- The recommended way to provide the API key is through the `NVIDIA_API_KEY` environment variable.\n\nRaises:\n    DeprecationWarning: If an API key is not provided for a hosted NIM, a warning is issued. This will become an error in version 0.2.0."]}, {"name": "llama_index.llms.nvidia.base.NVIDIA.__get_default_model", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Set default model."]}, {"name": "llama_index.llms.nvidia.base.NVIDIA._validate_url", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "base_url", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Base URL Validation.\nValueError : url which do not have valid scheme and netloc.\nWarning : v1/chat/completions routes.\nValueError : Any other routes other than above."]}, {"name": "llama_index.llms.nvidia.base.NVIDIA._validate_model", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "model_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Validates compatibility of the hosted model with the client.\n\nArgs:\n    model_name (str): The name of the model.\n\nRaises:\n    ValueError: If the model is incompatible with the client."]}, {"name": "llama_index.llms.nvidia.base.NVIDIA.available_models", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "List